<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Template</title>
    <style>
      /* Add your custom styles here */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f3f8fb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #1F2A40;
        color: #cbb269;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333333;
      }
      p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #666666;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #1F2A40;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #007bff;
      }
      hr {
        border: 0;
        border-top: 1px solid #cccccc;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Successful university registration</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>We hope this email finds you well. We are delighted to inform you that the registration of <%= @university %> on our platform has been successfully completed.</p>
        <hr>
        <p><strong>University Name:</strong> <%= @university %></p>
        <p><strong><%= link_to "Click here", @url + "/resetPassword?reset_password_token=#{@token}", class: 'button' %></strong> to get started.</p>
        <hr>
        <p>We believe that the addition of <%= @university %> will enhance our community and create new opportunities for collaboration and growth.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please feel free to contact us.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you for your support!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
